Robert Tudawali https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_Tudawali 0 Robert Tudawali (1929 – 26 July 1967) also known as Bobby Wilson was an Australian actor and indigenous activist, born and raised on Melville Island in the Northern Territory to Tiwi parents.
